---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Easier, breezier data - Breezey">
  <Nav />
  <main class="content-grid">
    <h1 class="content text-zinc-800 dark:text-gray-100 m-5">
      Easy Breezey Data
    </h1>
    <div
      class="cloud-container"
      :class="{'cloud-container': !darkMode, 'cloud-container-dark': darkMode }"
    >
      <div id="cloud-intro"></div>
    </div>
    <h2 class="content text-slate-700 dark:text-gray-200 m-5">
      Effortless Tagging, Limitless Insights.
    </h2>
    <h3 class="content text-zinc-600 dark:text-gray-400 m-5 max-w-lg">
      Experience lighter, faster data collection that out performs conventional
      tag managers. ðŸ“Š
    </h3>
    <section class="">
      <button
        class="content md:w-1/4 w-full text-gray-600 m-5 bg-gray-100 hover:bg-white py-2 px-4 border-b-4 border-gray-400 rounded-lg font-bold"
      >
        Learn More
      </button>
      <button
        class="content md:w-1/4 w-full bg-blue-500 m-5 hover:bg-blue-400 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 border-b-4 border-blue-700 rounded-lg hover:border-blue-500"
      >
        Sign Up
      </button>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-10">
      <h4 class="text-2xl text-center">Easy, Breezey Tag Management</h4>

      <p class="p-2">
        At Breezey, we're redefining the landscape of tag management. With our
        innovative reverse proxy approach, you can now experience tag management
        like never before. Our system stands apart, offering unparalleled
        reliability and efficiency.
      </p><h5 class="p-2">How it works:</h5>

      <ul>
        <li class="p-2">
          <strong>Unfailing Pageview Registration</strong>: Breezey's reverse
          proxy tag manager guarantees every pageview is captured, unaffected by
          adblockers. Never miss a beat in tracking user interactions.
        </li>
        <li class="p-2">
          <strong>Beyond Cookie Reliance</strong>: Our advanced technology
          operates independently of 3rd party, and even 1st party cookies. This
          paves the way for enhanced privacy and compliance with evolving data
          regulations.
        </li>
        
      <div class="max-w-lg my-10 mx-auto p-4 bg-white bg-opacity-30 shadow-lg rounded-lg">
        <blockquote class="italic text-zinc-800 text-lg">
            "'Effortless Tagging, Limitless Insights' isn't just a motto; it's
            what they deliver. Breezey is the future of data collection - 
            lighter, faster, and more reliable than ever."
        </blockquote>
        <cite class="block text-right text-sm text-black mt-4">- Liam Martin</cite>
    </div>
        <li class="p-2">
          <strong>Cloud-Based Execution</strong>: All tags are processed in the
          cloud, ensuring swift and accurate data delivery to your analytics
          tools. This method bypasses common browser-based pitfalls like slow
          internet, sluggish devices, and obstructive adblockers.
        </li>
        <li class="p-2">
          <strong>Dynamic Content Injection</strong>: Our system facilitates
          rapid content injection, enabling you to introduce dynamic,
          high-performance content seamlessly and efficiently.
        </li>
        <li class="p-2">
          <strong>AI-Driven Simplicity</strong>: Breezey harnesses the power of
          AI, reducing your dependence on web development teams. This means
          quicker, more streamlined tool integration and enhanced ease of use.
        </li>
        <li class="p-2">
          <strong>Reliable Conversion Tracking</strong>: With our system, every
          conversion is accurately captured and attributed to its source. This
          ensures reliable campaign reporting and easier, more dependable data
          collection.
        </li>
        <li class="p-2">
          <strong>Quick and Easy Trial & Integration</strong>: Try Breezey for
          free and witness its capabilities firsthand. Set up takes less than 10
          minutes, and it seamlessly integrates with your existing tag
          management solutions for a smooth transition.
        </li>
      </ul>
      
      <div class="max-w-lg my-10 mx-auto p-4 bg-white bg-opacity-30 shadow-lg rounded-lg">
        <blockquote class="italic text-zinc-800 text-lg">
            "We run campaigns using 10+ online advertisers. Our pages were getting bogged down with tags and our analytics were suffering. Breezey solved all of our problems. I'll never worry about missing conversions again!"
        </blockquote>
        <cite class="block text-right text-sm text-black mt-4">- Will Bremner</cite>
    </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .cloud-container {
    border-top: 2px solid rgb(180, 180, 180);
    border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(180, 180, 180);
    grid-column: full-width;
    height: 8rem;
    z-index: -10;
    background-color: #78bdff;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      #5d99d1 15%,
      #75b4ef 80%,
      #b8d3ec 100%
    );
  }

  .cloud-container-dark {
    border-top: 2px solid rgb(180, 180, 180);
    border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(180, 180, 180);
    grid-column: full-width;
    height: 8rem;
    z-index: -10;
    background-color: #2d3e50;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      #071d34 0%,
      #2d3e50 50%,
      #4b6b8a 75%,
      #6d8ea3 100%
    );
  }

  #cloud-intro {
    --cloud-1: 120px;
    --cloud-2: 200px;
    --cloud-3: 150px;
    --cloud-4: 0px;
    height: 100%;
    grid-column: full-width;
    background: url(/images/clouds1000.png);
    background:
      url(/images/clouds1000.png) 0 var(--cloud-1),
      url(/images/clouds1200_1.png) 0 var(--cloud-2),
      url(/images/clouds800_blur3.png) 0 var(--cloud-3),
      url(/images/logos1600.png) 0 var(--cloud-4);
    animation: windy 8s linear infinite;
    background-size: auto 150px;
  }

  @keyframes windy {
    0% {
      background-position:
        0 var(--cloud-1),
        0 var(--cloud-2),
        0 var(--cloud-3),
        0 var(--cloud-4);
    }

    100% {
      background-position:
        1000px var(--cloud-1),
        1200px var(--cloud-2),
        800px var(--cloud-3),
        1600px var(--cloud-4);
    }
  }
</style>
